<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - ResQ</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        h1 { border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        h2 { margin-top: 30px; color: #000; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 5px; }
        h3 { margin-top: 20px; color: #444; }
        p, li { margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .back-link { display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #4f46e5; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }
        .driver-policy-header { background: #f8fafc; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 50px; border-left: 4px solid #d97706; }
        .meta { color: #666; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        ul { padding-left: 20px; list-style-type: disc; }
        .footer-note { font-style: italic; color: #666; margin-top: 40px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 20px; }
        .copyright { text-align: center; color: #999; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <% if (!user) { %>
        <a href="/login" class="back-link">&larr; Back to Login</a>
    <% } else { %>
        <a href="/dashboard" class="back-link">&larr; Back to Dashboard</a>
    <% } %>

    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="meta">Last updated: April 2026</p>
    <p>Your privacy and data security are our top priorities.</p>

    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>RESQ respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and store your personal information when you use our platform or services. This policy complies with the Qatar Personal Data Privacy Protection Law (Law No. 13 of 2016).</p>

    <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <h3>A. Information You Provide</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Name, phone number, email</li>
        <li>Pickup and drop-off addresses</li>
        <li>Payment method (processed securely via local payment gateways)</li>
        <li>Feedback, reviews, and service ratings</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>B. Automatically Collected Information</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>GPS location (real-time during service use)</li>
        <li>IP address, device model, OS, app version</li>
        <li>App usage data and interaction logs</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>C. From Third Parties</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Apple or Google sign-in data (if used)</li>
        <li>Payment providers (confirmation of transaction status)</li>
        <li>Customer service tools</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use your personal data to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Match you with the closest available service provider</li>
        <li>Provide customer support and safety features (live tracking, verification)</li>
        <li>Process payments and generate receipts</li>
        <li>Send trip status notifications and service updates</li>
        <li>Improve our services through analytics</li>
        <li>Prevent fraud and abuse</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Sharing of Your Information</h2>
    <h3>A. Service Providers</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>RESQ drivers (to fulfill your request)</li>
        <li>Cloud hosting providers (e.g., AWS)</li>
        <li>Payment processors that support Apple Pay, Google Pay, Visa, and Mastercard in Qatar</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>B. Government Authorities</h3>
    <p>When legally required for security or regulatory purposes under Qatari law.</p>

    <h3>C. With Your Consent</h3>
    <p>If you explicitly agree to share information (e.g., promotions or referrals).</p>

    <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain your data only for as long as necessary to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Fulfill the purpose for which it was collected</li>
        <li>Meet legal, regulatory, tax, or accounting requirements</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You can request the deletion of your account and personal data unless required by law to retain it.</p>

    <h2>6. Security</h2>
    <p>We apply industry-standard security practices, including:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Data encryption in transit and at rest</li>
        <li>Secured authentication</li>
        <li>Access controls and continuous monitoring</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Under Qatari law, you have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Request access to your personal data</li>
        <li>Correct or delete your data</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
        <li>File a complaint with Qatar's data protection authority if your rights are violated</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>8. Location Services and Tracking</h2>
    <p>RESQ collects real-time location data to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Connect you with nearby drivers</li>
        <li>Ensure trip safety</li>
        <li>Verify pickup and drop-off</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Disabling location access will limit app functionality.</p>

    <h2>9. Cookies and App Analytics</h2>
    <p>We use cookies and in-app analytics tools to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Understand usage patterns</li>
        <li>Fix bugs and improve user experience</li>
        <li>Monitor performance</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You may disable cookies in your device settings.</p>

    <h2>10. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>RESQ is not intended for users under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect data from minors.</p>

    <h2>11. Updates to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Major changes will be communicated through the app or by email. Continued use of RESQ means you accept the updated policy.</p>

    <h2>12. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions, requests, or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us:</p>
    <p>
        <strong>RESQ Customer Support</strong><br>
        Phone: +974 7110 0016<br>
        Email: resq.qa@gmail.com
    </p>

    <div class="driver-policy-header">
        <h1 style="border:0; margin-bottom:10px;">Driver App Policies</h1>
    </div>

    <h2>1. Payouts and Withdrawal Policy</h2>
    <p>Drivers will receive their cleared earnings automatically every Sunday via transfer to their registered bank account. This is processed without the need for manual withdrawal requests, and no fees apply to this weekly automatic payout.</p>
    <p>However, if a driver chooses to request an early or manual withdrawal outside the weekly cycle, a 5% transaction fee will be applied to the withdrawn amount. To avoid this fee, drivers are advised to wait for the regular Sunday payout. No refunds will be issued for manually requested withdrawals once the transaction is processed.</p>

    <h2>2. Payment Processing Policy</h2>
    <h3>1. Standard Payment Schedule</h3>
    <p>All client payments are processed every Sunday as part of our regular payment cycle. This service is included at no additional charge.</p>

    <h3>2. Requests for Off-Cycle Payments</h3>
    <p>If a client requests payment on any day other than Sunday, the request requires additional administrative work, manual system handling, and staff time.</p>

    <h3>3. Service Fee for Off-Cycle Payments</h3>
    <p>Due to the extra operational effort required, an additional service fee of 5% will be applied to the total payment amount for any off-cycle payment request.</p>

    <h3>4. Purpose of the Fee</h3>
    <p>This fee is not related to the timing of the payment itself. It is solely intended to cover the extra labor, system processing, and operational costs associated with handling payments outside the standard schedule.</p>

    <h3>5. Client Agreement</h3>
    <p>By using our services, the client acknowledges and agrees to this payment processing policy, including the service fee for off-cycle payment requests.</p>

    <p class="footer-note">By using ResQ Driver app, you agree to these policies.</p>
    <p class="copyright">&copy; 2026 RESQ Qatar. All rights reserved.</p>
</body>
</html>
